00:31:48.136 --> 00:31:49.470
r bigger than R.
 

00:31:49.470 --> 00:31:50.960
Student:
&gt;

00:31:50.960 --> 00:31:51.420
Oh, gotcha.
 

00:31:51.420 --> 00:31:53.244
Prof: Oh,
