00:32:51.868 --> 00:32:56.959
Student:  Why we
________ 4 pi squared times E of

00:32:56.959 --> 00:32:57.328
r.
 

00:32:57.328 --> 00:32:58.420
Prof: Why do I do that
you mean?

00:32:58.420 --> 00:32:59.000
Student:  Yeah.
 

00:32:59.000 --> 00:33:00.846
Prof: Right.
 

00:33:00.846 --> 00:33:05.220
So the correct way to do it is
