01:10:52.560 --> 01:10:56.640
You're supposed to take
dxdy you write it like

01:10:56.640 --> 01:10:57.189
this.
 

01:10:57.189 --> 01:10:58.279
There's no function or integral.
 

01:10:58.279 --> 01:11:01.282
I just want 1 times
dxdy, so the 1 is

01:11:01.282 --> 01:11:02.050
implicit.
 

01:11:02.050 --> 01:11:08.078
dy, you pick a certain
x and y should go

01:11:08.078 --> 01:11:10.090
